cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.CL, cs.LG. 

The paper focuses on cross-media retrieval, which involves computer vision (image and video), natural language processing (text), and audio processing. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are also relevant due to the multi-modal nature of the task. Finally, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible sub-category since the paper proposes a deep learning model for the task.
